      * >>PRE-COMPILER<<                                                    *
      *                                                                     *
      *   >>CRTCMD<< CRTRPGMOD    MODULE(&LI/&OB) +                         *
      *                           SRCFILE(&SL/&SF) +                        *
      *                           SRCMBR(&SM);                              *
      *                                                                     *
      *   >>COMPILE<<                                                       *
      *     >>PARM<< TRUNCNBR(*NO);                                         *
      *     >>PARM<< DBGVIEW(*LIST);                                        *
